data.description: Attractive, 3/2 home with a NEW ROOF in an excellent Cape Coral neighborhood, close to restaurants and attractions of downtown Fort Myers and shopping of Pine Island corridor!  Expansive, fenced back yard complete with a storage shed.  Nicely landscaped, this home shows well!  Kitchen is open to the family/dining area and has stainless steel appliances, travertine backsplash, pass-through window to the screened lanai and pantry.  There's a formal living area as you enter the home, plenty of space to entertain!  Master bedroom is spacious and has a walk-in closet while the 2 guest bedrooms are split from the master.  One of the guest bedrooms has access to the screened lanai through through sliding glass doors.  A great place to call home, second home or investment property!  HVAC new in 2017 and roof just completed!  City utilities in and all assessments paid!   Minutes to downtown Cape Coral and an easy drive to Fort Myers Beach and Sanibel. This one won't last long, call today to schedule your private showing!
